HEADWORD: Branchy
<hw>Branch"y</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Full of branches;
having wide-spreading branches; consisting of branches.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Beneath thy <qex>branchy</qex> bowers of thickest gloom.</q>
<rj><qau>J. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

